==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Figurehead
<hw>Fig"ure*head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>The figure, statue, or bust, on the prow of a
ship.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person who allows his name to be used to give
standing to enterprises in which he has no responsible interest or
duties; a nominal, but not real, head or chief.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Figurial</ent>⟦br⟧
